Language: Python
Libraries:
	Data Processing → pandas, numpy
	•	PDF Parsing → PyPDF2, pdfplumber
	•	OCR (if statements are scanned) → pytesseract, opencv-python
	•	Machine Learning → scikit-learn, xgboost, tensorflow (for prediction)
	•	Visualization → matplotlib, seaborn, or plotly
	•	Dashboard (optional) → Streamlit or Flask
	•	Storage: Local CSV or SQLite (for now)
	•	IDE: VS Code or Jupyter Notebook
